VPC Perring 
same availability zone or another zone 

Create 2 VPC
Configure IGW, Subnet, Route table

Peering connections 

1 vpc will be send req to second vpc for accepting 

configure to route table 
so edit route in 1 vpc and click add route 
enter the second vpc route table subnet ip in vpc 1 , target peering

same configuration will be second vpc

so edit route in second vpc and click add route 
enter the 1 vpc route table subnet ip in vpc 2, target peering

now configuration is done 

Note: when you launching instance you have to configure security groups ssh, All traffic
then your perring will be successfully ping with 1 vpc instance to another vpc instance using private ip.
